## Contact

**DLRA (Defense Language Research Agency) is headquartered in Singapore. The organization works with defense intelligence agencies, maritime domain awareness organizations, and national security institutions on domain-specific AI systems for intelligence processing.**


<blockquote>
  <p>"At the heart of interoperability between nations is trust and cooperation. Technology is partially the solution, but the more challenging part is the cooperation — and that cooperation is what creates enduring advantage."</p>
</blockquote>


## Inquiries

For inquiries about DLRA products, technology partnerships, or evaluation deployments:

**Email:** contact@dlra-research.org

## Areas of Engagement

| Engagement Type | Description |
|----------------|-------------|
| Product evaluation | Controlled deployment of Threat Lens, Maritime NLP, or SynthBrief against operational baselines |
| Technology partnership | Collaborative development of domain-specific retrieval and generation capabilities |
| Research collaboration | Joint benchmarking, evaluation framework development, defense NLP research |
| Sovereign deployment planning | Infrastructure assessment for on-premise or national cloud deployment |

## Location

**Singapore**

DLRA is headquartered in Singapore with a focus on defense technology applications across the Asia-Pacific region and with allied defense organizations.

